snippet.title: the 99 nights frogs are mean! but not real ones... :D
snippet.description:
JOIN THE FAM - https://www.youtube.com/@GforGaming

HEY EVERYBODY!! 

The new frog update in 99 Nights in the Forest is crazy! All of the frogs are out to get you! Niko wishes they didn't even exist!... But, maybe just in Roblox! Because real frogs are cool!
